                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18241028-57-off306 t18241028-57-cd307"></join>, ten silver spoons, value 3 l., and a pair of sugar tongs, value 5 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18241028-57-victim567" type="victimName">
